<div class="page">
	<div id="content" class="page-container container" style="padding-top:22px">
		<header class="header">
			
			<h1 class="title" align="left">
				武平的这里，不仅有千年古道，还有你未曾领略的美景~
			</h1>
			<div class="desc">
				<img src="//om.gtimg.cn/om/om_3.0/h5_detail/images/logo_qiehao.png" class="logo">
				<span class="author">文旅武平</span>
				<span class="date">2019-12-06</span>
			</div>
			
		</header>
		<section class="article">
			

			

			
		
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298612/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298612/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>光阴荏苒，武平的崇山峻岭中，先人用汗水铺出了一条条山道，历尽沧桑的古道曾承载着村庄间的文明交流。而今，古道已是一种情怀，怀揣着先人的脚印在山间顾自沉淀。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298613/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298613/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>周末，我们一起走进大岭脑古道，聆听它的故事，感受曾经的喧闹与繁华。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298614/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298614/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>早上下了大雨，既然决定出发，那就风雨无阻。车行至尧禄村，雨竟然停了。驴友们从一片幽谷清秀的竹林起步，旁边是一个不大的池塘。空山新雨后，清风徐来，竹叶沙沙随风起舞，不远处的天马寨被一朵雨做的云环绕着，幽雅空灵。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298615/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298615/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>这条古道是从前中堡、武东的人们去往武平县城的必经之路，大部分路面宽一米有余，目前石阶保存得较好。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298616/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298616/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>踏着石阶沿山而上，古道旁的山涧蜿蜒开去，时而陡峭时而平缓，悦耳的鸟鸣，吟唱的溪流，合着行人踏叶的沙沙声，仿佛让人听到了古道的前世今生。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298617/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298617/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298618/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298618/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>一路上古树参天，有的树龄都在数百年以上，苍劲古朴，极具原始森林风貌。古道与古树，伫立千年守望乡土，同时与古村落相映成趣，别有一番美感。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298619/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298619/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>350年树龄的罗汉松</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298620/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298620/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298621/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298621/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>正值芒种时节，农人在梯田间耕种，黄发孩童嬉笑其间，鸡犬之声相闻，村内屋舍俨然，良田阡陌纵横、层层叠叠。古树、古道、清泉、密林，白云缭绕，群峰叠嶂，犹胜世外桃源。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298622/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298622/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298623/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298623/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298624/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298624/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>古道尽头的村落，竟藏着一些古老的建筑。因年久失修，往昔的繁华已不复存在。然而，那些萧瑟的残垣断壁、青苔斑驳的大宅门、高高翘起的屋檐以及清澈见底的圆井，见证了历史的沧海桑田，别样的风情让人久久不忍离去！</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298625/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10869298625/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
